INSTALLATION
============

You have two choices to install.

*  As an app inside a project
*  As an app within Python's site-packages

To include as a app within a project:

*  Copy the ``rest2pdf`` directory to your Django project directory.
*  Include ``rest2pdf`` as an INSTALLED_APP.
*  To your project settings.py file, add:

# List of rst2pdf style sheet paths.
RST2PDF_STYLESHEET_DIRS = ['proj/rest2pdf/styles',]

Dependencies
------------

rst2pdf
ReportLab

Python and Django Versions
--------------------------

Tested on:

   Python 2.6
   Django 1.1.1